<note n="0083001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0083001">【原】慶安四年刊宗教大學藏本，【甲】大谷大學藏金陵刻本</note>
<note n="0083002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0083002">（唐）＋帝【甲】</note>
